This is a user-friendly object-oriented wrapper for TokyoCabinet HDB & BDB.
Methods with obscure arguments accept both options hash and old fashion arguments.
Failed methods raise TokyoCabinet::Error instead of returning false.

AUTHORSHIP

  Initial author: Oleg Andreev <oleganza@gmail.com>
  Date: August 22, 2008.

